
Sharpedo	 A water type Pokémon

Nicknamed “the bully of the 
sea,” SHARPEDO is widely feared. 
 Its cruel fangs grow back immediately 
if they snap off.  Just one of 
these Pokémon can thoroughly 
tear apart a supertanker. 

